  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Transportation;  Requiring the Department of Transportation and any impacted local government to increase the minimum perception-reaction time for steady yellow signals at certain intersections by a specified amount of time; authorizing enforcement of restrictive school zone speed limits through the use of speed detection systems under certain conditions; revising provisions relating to the placement and installation of certain speed detection systems and components thereof; revising a limitation on the use of videos and images recorded as part of a school bus infraction detection system; revising provisions relating to penalties for certain failures to comply, etc."
    }
  ],
